[{"id":"ai-sug-Fp8fup3adv62hy5ficH-I","type":"h1","children":[{"text":"Mastering Copilot: A Complete Guide"}]},{"id":"5-HsH6tQIl","type":"toc","children":[{"text":""}]},{"id":"zHbNtF6LzN","type":"p","children":[{"text":"Copilot is an advanced AI-powered writing assistant that integrates seamlessly into your workflow. By leveraging machine learning models, it predicts your next words and provides context-aware suggestions to accelerate your content creation process."}]},{"id":"_SV3YbnUb5","icon":"🚀","type":"callout","children":[{"id":"N2ZSFP8Ibv","type":"p","children":[{"text":"Pro Tip: The more context you provide through clear headings and consistent formatting, the more accurate Copilot's suggestions become.","italic":true}]}],"backgroundColor":"#f0f9ff"},{"id":"ai-sug-Q_BbKk8qQTg9lmkHZI0YY","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Provide clear headings"}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"ai-sug-7IC7hPDeFz2wq-Ej3TVxv","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Use consistent formatting"}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"ai-sug-JzNqcMVc3vZUaon2BvjsM","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Improve Copilot's accuracy"}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"DyGXDUJI9F","type":"h2","children":[{"text":"Understanding Suggestion Triggers"}]},{"id":"ai-sug-csrffzih_6znoLd9r1KnL","type":"column_group","children":[{"id":"UrZCpRrDtT","type":"column","width":"50%","children":[{"id":"yCIVAX1hXL","type":"h3","children":[{"text":"Automatic Mode"}]},{"id":"7EacmINp2q","type":"p","children":[{"text":"Automatic Mode operates seamlessly in the background, analyzing your current context, comments, and function signatures in real-time. As you type, Copilot predicts the most likely next steps and presents them as 'ghost text'—a light-gray suggestion that doesn't interfere with your existing code."}]},{"id":"qUTDYHAzAC","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Accept suggestions instantly by pressing the "},{"bold":true,"code":true,"text":"Tab"},{"bold":true,"text":" key."}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"xZ7UWj92Sf","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Reduces repetitive typing by predicting boilerplate and common patterns."}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"HpnrIcPDQr","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Continuously learns from your local project structure to provide contextually relevant completions."}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"}]},{"id":"tBcuGBes0A","type":"column","width":"50%","children":[{"id":"rd1_iPjoj2","type":"h3","children":[{"text":"Manual Mode"}]},{"id":"ub7-FBP0j3","type":"p","children":[{"text":"Manual Mode gives you full control over when the AI intervenes, which is ideal for complex architectural decisions or when you're looking for creative inspiration. Instead of waiting for the auto-trigger, you can explicitly request suggestions at any cursor position."}]},{"id":"9FT31Tz_n-","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Trigger suggestions on demand using shortcuts like "},{"bold":true,"code":true,"text":"Alt + \\"},{"bold":true,"text":" (Windows) or "},{"bold":true,"code":true,"text":"Option + \\"},{"bold":true,"text":" (macOS)."}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"xp7m2QnbE_","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Cycle through multiple alternative suggestions to find the best fit for your specific logic."}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"C02QBFcS0i","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Perfect for generating entire function bodies or complex data structures from a single descriptive comment."}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"}]}]},{"id":"0aM4_MDF6m","type":"h2","children":[{"text":"Essential Keyboard Shortcuts"}]},{"id":"TZJ5IYowTU","type":"table","children":[{"id":"AbGp_QHsuj","type":"tr","children":[{"id":"z-7xzZvHBe","type":"th","children":[{"id":"0gja98tdbx","type":"p","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Action"}]}]},{"id":"hA8LOlQzIV","type":"th","children":[{"id":"U8e29ImhE3","type":"p","children":[{"bold":tr