enerated code or facts before final implementation to ensure accuracy."}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"kn-2","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Use clear and descriptive variable or heading names to provide better context for the AI."}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"kn-3","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Copilot performs exceptionally well with widely used languages like Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript."}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"kn-4","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"You can customize privacy settings to disable Copilot for specific sensitive files or directories."}],"listStart":4,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"kn-5","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"The AI adapts to your specific coding or writing style within the context of your current session."}],"listStart":5,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"kn-6","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Regularly update your IDE extension to access the latest performance improvements and features."}],"listStart":6,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"trouble-h2","type":"h2","children":[{"text":"Troubleshooting Common Issues"}]},{"id":"tr-1","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Suggestions not appearing: "},{"text":"Verify your subscription status and ensure the 'Inline Suggestions' setting is enabled in your IDE."}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"tr-2","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Slow response times: "},{"text":"Check your network latency; Copilot requires a stable connection to communicate with the cloud models."}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"tr-3","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Incorrect completions: "},{"text":"Provide more context by writing a comment describing the specific logic or function you want to create."}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"faq-h2","type":"h2","children":[{"text":"Frequently Asked Questions"}]},{"id":"ai-sug-akXQW8UpsAx1yRSN7n2P2","type":"h3","children":[{"text":"Troubleshooting GitHub Copilot Issues"}]},{"id":"ai-sug-ggjqmy_GVi3R-EHMvTKyV","type":"p","children":[{"text":"To resolve common issues and optimize your experience with GitHub Copilot, consider the following detailed steps:"}]},{"id":"ai-sug-ts8MnfVUMqq8uHFFLv31I","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Verify Subscription Status: "},{"text":"Ensure your GitHub Copilot subscription is active by checking your billing settings on GitHub. If you are using a business or enterprise account, confirm that your administrator has assigned a seat to your user profile."}],"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"ai-sug-bzO1blzLaHGCyLabFBQi6","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Maintain a Stable Connection: "},{"text":"Copilot relies on real-time communication with cloud-based models. If you experience latency or 'disconnected' errors, check your firewall or proxy settings to ensure that the IDE can reach GitHub's API endpoints."}],"listStart":2,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"ai-sug--CKKWS220M42qjbf9C1Pz","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Optimize Contextual Awareness: "},{"text":"The AI performs best when it has context. Keep related files open in adjacent tabs, use descriptive variable names, and write detailed comments before your code blocks to help the model predict the logic you intend to implement."}],"listStart":3,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"ai-sug-ZNavANAcBwpXryD57YNHD","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Update the Extension: "},{"text":"Regularly update the Copilot extension in your IDE (such as VS Code or JetBrains) to ensure compatibility with the latest API changes and to access new features and performance patches."}],"listStart":4,"listStyleType":"disc"},{"id":"faq-1-q","type":"p","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Is my code kept private?"}]},{"id":"faq-1-a","type":"p","children":[{"text":"Yes, enterprise versions of Copilot provide robust privacy protections to ensure your proprietary code remains secure and is not used to train public models."}]},{"id":"faq-2-q","type":"p","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Does it work offline?"}]},{"id":"ai-sug-8biRBbppU0gtq1Rn2P71p","type":"p","indent":1,"children":[{"text":"Requires an internet connection for real-time cloud suggestions."}],"listStyleType":"disc"}]